survey.music_making: Self-taught bass player. Played in garage bands, kegger parties, etc. in Southern California during the "hair metal explosion" 1977 - 1984 (ish). Played in a couple basic rock cover bands after that. Haven't played with anybody in a good 25, 30 years now. But I still jam to my self and am constantly trying to learn/write new stuff.
survey.habit_change: Some older stuff I used to like, I don't care for as much anymore. Some older stuff I used to not care for, I appreciate a lot more these days. And I'm always on the listen-out for new/unique upcoming artists.
